  </ul>
</p>


<h2>Security</h2>
<p>
  We've done what we can to keep your data secure, we store as little
  information as possible to limit the danger. Only one person (the
  above mentioned owner) has access to the data.
</p>

<h2>Cookies</h2>

<p>
  We use a single session cookie to identify you, and Google does too.
  We don't use cookies for anything else than identifying that you're
  authenticated.
</p>
  
